3727:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****               (+++) Enables automatic calibration and frequency error counter feature
3728:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****            Note: When using USB LPM (Link Power Management) and the device is in Sleep mode, the
3729:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****            periodic USB SOF will not be generated by the host. No SYNC signal will therefore be
3730:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****            provided to the CRS to calibrate the HSI48 on the run. To guarantee the required clock
3731:Drivers/STM32U5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32u5xx_hal_rcc_ex.c ****            precision after waking up from Sleep mode, the LSE or reference clock on the GPIOs
